cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with 3D shape recognition using deep learning methods based on point-cloud and multi-view data. It may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories as it proposes a fusion network based on multimodal attention mechanism for improving recognition accuracy. Additionally, it may belong to the graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories as it deals with 3D data and image processing.
